{"about_the_game":"<strong>This version contains some cards and the content of Chapter 1</strong><br><br><strong>Welcome to the Magic Brick Realm! As a new adventurer, you need to defeat various monster enemies here through brick duel.</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243920/extras/1y.png?t=1729753444\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243920/extras/1z.gif?t=1729753444\" /><br><strong> In a single game, the enemy and you will play monster bricks on the board one after another during the round. Choose your strategy carefully and try to occupy more plots to gain more points. The side with the higher score at the end of the game will win! </strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243920/extras/2y.png?t=1729753444\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243920/extras/2z.gif?t=1729753444\" /><br><strong> Monster bricks are the main units in the battle. They have different images, sizes and skills. Sometimes they will also produce different numbers of arcane bricks as a continuation of their influence, helping you occupy more land. .<br>However, it should be noted that arcane bricks tend to be more fragile, and you need to choose to place them more carefully. </strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243920/extras/3y.png?t=1729753444\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243920/extras/3z.gif?t=1729753444\" /><br><strong> Various terrains may appear in a single game. Learn to take advantage of these terrains, or stay away from bad terrains. Will these terrains make your plan more effective or a mess? </strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.a